    <item>
      <title>土耳其货币市场基金面临 29 亿美元里拉债券热潮</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/turkey-money-market-funds-face-2-9-billion-push-into-lira-bonds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其出台新要求，要求货币市场基金将其投资组合的至少 10% 配置给政府债券，此举将引来数十亿里拉资金投入国债，从而推高对收益率曲线短端的需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/turkey-money-market-funds-face-2-9-billion-push-into-lira-bonds</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 10:49:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>UniCredit 的 BPM Curveball 让 Meloni 的银行计划陷入困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/orcel-s-bpm-curveball-leaves-meloni-scrambling-on-banking-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利联合信贷银行 (UniCredit SpA) 出人意料地竞购 Banco BPM SpA，这让意大利总理乔治亚·梅洛尼 (Giorgia Meloni) 的政府感到困惑，他们创建意大利第三大银行集团的计划是否已经失败。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/orcel-s-bpm-curveball-leaves-meloni-scrambling-on-banking-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 10:44:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国银行预计新兴市场货币将下跌 5%，因贸易战风险被低估</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/bofa-sees-5-em-currency-slide-as-trade-war-risks-underpriced</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行策略师表示，投资者低估了唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 担任总统期间的贸易战风险，他们预测新兴市场货币将在 2025 年上半年下跌 5%，主权债务将遭到抛售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/bofa-sees-5-em-currency-slide-as-trade-war-risks-underpriced</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 10:41:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Orcel 放弃德国商业银行，转而追求 Banco BPM</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/orcel-signals-bpm-move-lowers-urgency-to-pursue-commerzbank-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利联合信贷银行 (UniCredit SpA) 首席执行官 Andrea Orcel 表示，在他开始在本土市场发起收购竞标后，收购德国商业银行并不是他目前的首要任务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/orcel-signals-bpm-move-lowers-urgency-to-pursue-commerzbank-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 09:27:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫迪领导的政党赢得关键州选举，印度股市延续涨势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/india-stocks-extend-rally-as-modi-s-party-wins-key-state-polls</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪领导的印度人民党领导的联盟在印度最富裕的马哈拉施特拉邦取得压倒性胜利，印度股市基准指数周一飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-25/india-stocks-extend-rally-as-modi-s-party-wins-key-state-polls</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 04:02:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
